How to use this image as a IPSec VPN client
============================================================

1. It's useful to create an alias for running this image

echo "alias charon-cmd='docker run --rm -it --net host --cap-add=NET_ADMIN strongswan'" >> ~/.bashrc

2. Then we can "charon-cmd" as per-normal, substitue USER and REMOTE_VPN_HOST accordingyly

charon-cmd --cert isrgrootx1.pem.txt --cert letsencryptauthorityx3.pem.txt \
--ike-proposal aes256-sha1-modp1024 \
--identity USER --host REMOTE_VPN_HOST